{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T09:01:53.259Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "RMSProp — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What RMSProp Is"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "RMSProp (Root Mean Square Propagation)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is an adaptive learning rate optimizer that adjusts the learning rate for each parameter based on its recent gradient history. It was developed independently around the same time as AdaGrad, specifically to address the "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "rapid decay problem"}, {"type": "text", "text": " in AdaGrad where learning rates become infinitesimally small."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The key innovation is using an "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "exponentially decaying moving average"}, {"type": "text", "text": " of squared gradients instead of accumulating all past squared gradients, giving more weight to recent information and effectively \"forgetting\" the distant past."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why RMSProp Matters in Generative AI"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp is widely used in major deep learning frameworks and excels in specific scenarios:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Use Case"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why RMSProp Works"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Superior convergence for sequence modeling"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Deep Neural Networks"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Handles high curvature and noisy gradients"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Non-stationary problems"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Adapts to changing gradient magnitudes"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Sparse data"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Handles sparse gradients effectively"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Video generation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Temporal models benefit from adaptive learning rates"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How RMSProp Works"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The Problem with AdaGrad"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "AdaGrad"}, {"type": "text", "text": " accumulates all squared gradients:"}]}, {"type": "blockMath", "attrs": {"latex": "G_t = G_{t-1} + g_t^{2}"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Problem: The sum grows continuously, causing the effective learning rate to shrink monotonically and eventually become infinitesimally small. This can "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "prematurely stop learning"}, {"type": "text", "text": " in deep learning."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp's Solution"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp uses an "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "exponentially decaying moving average"}, {"type": "text", "text": " instead of a sum:"}]}, {"type": "blockMath", "attrs": {"latex": "E[g^{2}]_t = \\beta \\times E[g^{2}]_{t-1} + (1 - \\beta) \\times g_t^{2}"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where:\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "g_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Gradient at time step t\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "E[g^{2}]_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Moving average of squared gradients\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\beta"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Decay rate (typically 0.9 to 0.99)"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Parameter Update Rule"}]}, {"type": "blockMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\theta_{t+1} = \\theta_t - \\frac{\\eta}{\\sqrt{E[g^{2}]_t + \\epsilon}} \\times g_t"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where:\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\theta_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Model parameter at time step t\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\eta"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Global learning rate\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\epsilon"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Small constant (e.g., "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "10^{-8}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ") for numerical stability\n- "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\sqrt{E[g^{2}]_t + \\epsilon}"}}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Adaptive scaling term"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Features"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "1. Adaptive Learning Rate per Parameter"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Parameter"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Gradient Magnitude"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "E[g^{2}]"}}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Effective LR"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Effect"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "W1"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Large oscillations"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Large"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Small"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Dampens oscillations"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "W2"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Small/stable"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Small"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Large"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Accelerates convergence"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Large gradients recently"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "E[g^{2}]"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " large → effective LR smaller → reduces oscillations"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Small gradients recently"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "E[g^{2}]"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " small → effective LR larger → accelerates learning"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "2. Forgets Distant Past"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The exponentially decaying average ensures "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "E[g^{2}]_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " is "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "dominated by more recent squared gradients"}, {"type": "text", "text": "."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "If gradients become small after initially being large, "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "E[g^{2}]_t"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " decreases over time, allowing the effective learning rate to "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "potentially increase again"}, {"type": "text", "text": "."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Unlike AdaGrad where learning rate remains suppressed, RMSProp adapts to recent gradient magnitude."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "3. Hyperparameters"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Hyperparameter"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Typical Value"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Purpose"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "η (learning rate)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "0.001"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Global step size"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "β (decay rate)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "0.9 or 0.99"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Memory of moving average"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "ε (epsilon)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "10^{-8}"}}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Numerical stability"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "momentum"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "0.0 (default)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Optional momentum term"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp in PyTorch"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Basic Usage"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "import torch\nimport torch.optim as optim\n\n# Model\nmodel = torch.nn.Linear(10, 1)\n\n# RMSProp optimizer\noptimizer = optim.RMSprop(\n    model.parameters(),\n    lr=0.001,       # Learning rate η [web:145]\n    alpha=0.99,     # Decay factor β (0.9-0.99) [web:145]\n    eps=1e-08       # Epsilon for stability [web:145]\n)\n\n# Training loop\nfor data, target in dataset:\n    output = model(data)\n    loss = torch.nn.MSELoss()(output, target)\n    \n    optimizer.zero_grad()\n    loss.backward()\n    optimizer.step()  # RMSProp update [web:145]"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "With Momentum"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# RMSProp with momentum (improves convergence)\noptimizer = optim.RMSprop(\n    model.parameters(),\n    lr=0.001,\n    alpha=0.99,\n    eps=1e-08,\n    momentum=0.9      # Add momentum term [web:146]\n)"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp in TensorFlow/Keras"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "import tensorflow as tf\n\n# RMSProp optimizer\noptimizer = tf.keras.optimizers.RMSprop(\n    learning_rate=0.001,  # Learning rate η [web:145]\n    rho=0.9,              # Decay factor β [web:146]\n    epsilon=1e-7,         # Epsilon [web:146]\n    momentum=0.9          # Momentum term [web:146]\n)\n\n# Training\nmodel.fit(\n    train_data,\n    train_labels,\n    epochs=100,\n    optimizer=optimizer\n)"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Comparison with AdaGrad and Adam"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp vs. AdaGrad"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "AdaGrad"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Accumulation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Sum of all squared gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Moving average (forgets past)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Learning rate decay"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Monotonically decreases to zero"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Adapts to recent gradients"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Long training"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Can stop prematurely"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Continues effectively"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Use case"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Convex problems"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Non-convex deep learning"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp vs. Adam"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Adam"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Components"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Adaptive LR only"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Adaptive LR + Momentum"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Parameters"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "lr, β, ε"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "lr, β₁, β₂, ε"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "RNNs"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Often better"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Can work, but RMSProp preferred"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Transformers"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Less common"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Standard (AdamW)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Hyperparameters"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Less tuning"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "More tuning but robust"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Adam combines "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Momentum + RMSProp"}, {"type": "text", "text": " and is the most superior optimizer that robustly adapts to large datasets and deep networks."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Momentum vs. RMSProp"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Momentum"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Adaptivity"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "No (single global LR)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Yes (per-parameter LR)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Direction"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Smooths path (accelerates)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Scales learning rate"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Oscillations"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Dampens via velocity"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Dampens via small LR for large gradients"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Flat regions"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Keeps moving via velocity"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Increases LR for small gradients"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Combined"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Momentum + RMSProp = Adam"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": " "}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Challenges and Trade-offs"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Challenge 1: Learning Rate Sensitivity"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp generally requires less tuning than SGD, but finding good values for η and β can still influence performance."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Typical values"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- Start with η = 0.001\n- β = 0.9 (default) or 0.99 for longer memory"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Challenge 2: No Momentum (Default)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The Keras RMSProp implementation uses "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "plain momentum, not Nesterov momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": ". Without momentum, it may converge slower than Adam."}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Solution"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Add momentum term:"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "optimizer = optim.RMSprop(momentum=0.9)  # Add momentum [web:146]"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "When to Use RMSProp"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "✅ "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Best for"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "RNNs and sequence models"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Deep neural networks"}, {"type": "text", "text": " with high curvature\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Non-stationary problems"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (changing gradient magnitudes)\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Sparse data"}, {"type": "text", "text": " or noisy gradients\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Video generation"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (temporal models)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "❌ "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Not ideal for"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Transformers/LLMs"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (AdamW is standard)\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Simple tasks"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (SGD or Adam may work better)\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "When you need both momentum + adaptivity"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (use Adam)"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Mental Model"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Think of RMSProp as "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "adjusting your step size based on terrain"}, {"type": "text", "text": ":"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Steep, rocky slope (large gradients)"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Take smaller steps (learning rate decreases) to avoid overshooting"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Flat, smooth path (small gradients)"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Take larger steps (learning rate increases) to move faster"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Remember recent terrain"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Only care about recent slope, not how it was 100 steps ago (\"forget\" distant past)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Adaptive per direction"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Each parameter (weight) has its own step size based on its gradient history"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Unlike AdaGrad (which gets stuck because it remembers too much), RMSProp "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "adapts continuously"}, {"type": "text", "text": " to recent conditions."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Takeaways"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "RMSProp"}, {"type": "text", "text": " = Adaptive learning rate optimizer using moving average of squared gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Update formula"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "\\theta_{t+1} = \\theta_t - \\frac{\\eta}{\\sqrt{E[g^{2}]_t + \\epsilon}} \\times g_t"}}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Moving average"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "E[g^{2}]_t = \\beta E[g^{2}]_{t-1} + (1 - \\beta) g_t^{2}"}}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Solves AdaGrad problem"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Prevents learning rate from shrinking to zero"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Forgets distant past"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Exponentially decaying average gives weight to recent gradients"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Adaptive per parameter"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Each weight has its own learning rate based on gradient history"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Hyperparameters"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": lr (η=0.001), decay (β=0.9-0.99), epsilon (ε=1e-8)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "RNNs"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Often better than Adam for recurrent networks"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Non-stationary"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Handles changing gradient magnitudes effectively"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "PyTorch"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "optim.RMSprop(lr=0.001, alpha=0.99, eps=1e-08)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "With momentum"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Add "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "code"}], "text": "momentum=0.9"}, {"type": "text", "text": " for faster convergence"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Adam = Momentum + RMSProp"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Combines both for best performance"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Transformers"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Less common (AdamW preferred)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "RMSProp is a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "foundational adaptive optimizer"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that prevents premature learning stop and adapts to recent gradient magnitudes, making it significantly more effective for training deep neural networks over extended periods than AdaGrad."}]}]}}